# MTGHelper
Open Project
=============================================
Andrew Diamond
John Lascha
Landon Rogers
=============================================
Magic: The Gathering Helper
=============================================
How to run:
  Start application
  Press "New Game"
  Select which format (Commander or Standard)
  Select how many players and press "Start Game"
  Use buttons to keep track of counters and health
There are information buttons everywhere for use 
with beginners.
=============================================
Known bugs:
  Runtime glitch when clicking the energy counter 
  button, moves the button itself over, something 
  to do with the relative layout for the xml file
No known crashes or errors, some warnings inside of
the xml files with the alignment
